dct_title_s: Slopes Greater Than 12% Dane County, Wisconsin 1995
dct_description_sm: This polygon data layer represents slopes greater than 12% in Dane County, Wisconsin in 1995. The dataset was originally published by the Dane County Land Information Office in 2005 using data from the Madison Area Transportation Planning Board.[Polygons representing slopes greater than or equal to 12% in Dane County, Wisocinsin. Derived from 10' resolution LiDAR bare-earth digital elevation model (DEM). Polygons were created and generalized in ArcGIS.]
